-                "No profitable public unwind route was discoverable from the live n00d/WETH source pair into any pre-existing n00d/WETH or n00d/<quote> venue reachable through the built-in Uniswap v2 and Uniswap v3 search set at the fork block, so the verifier could not settle the flashswap without inventing off-context liquidity.";
